						   <li style="margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px;">b. For cocks weighing 2.2 kg or lower, the allowed weight as give or take shall be 30 grams and for cocks weighing more than 2.2 kg, the allowed weight as give or take shall be 50 grams.</li>

